description: Details of design and external appearance pursuant to outline permission ref. 06/02433 granted on appeal for four storey block with accommodation in roof (Block A), four storey block with basement car park for 33 cars (and motorcycle/ bicycle parking) (Block B) and three storey block with accommodation in roof (Block C) comprising 129 flats (73 one bedroom, 48 two bedroom, 8 three bedroom) and 71 surface car parking spaces; widening of the 2 existing vehicular accesses and formation of pedestrian access.
